Titolo: Elevate (video game)

Anno: 2018

Descrizione: Elevate is an edutainment brain-training video game developed by Elevate Labs focusing on literacy and numeracy.
The brain-training genre having reached popularity with 2005's Brain Age, Lumosity would become one of top brain-training apps with 50 millions users, spawning a host of similar entries. In 2018, consumers spent an estimated $1.9 billion on brain training apps such as Lumosity, Peak and Elevate.Common Sense Media wrote that the game contains "speedy, amusing games sharpen speed but not grammar skills". Cnet conducted a comprehensive comparison of Lumosity and Elevate.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
